    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "THE LAY OF MILON",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000004_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000004_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "I purpose in this place to show you the story of Milon, and-since few words are best-I will set out the adventure as briefly as I may.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "So great was his prowess that from the day he was dubbed knight there was no champion who could stand before him in the lists.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "He was a passing fair knight, open and brave, courteous to his friends, and stern to his foes.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000005_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000005_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "Since he was praised by the frank, he was therefore envied of the mean.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000005_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000005_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "Nevertheless, by reason of his skill with the spear, he was counted a very worshipful knight, and was honourably entreated by many a prince in divers lands.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "With this baron dwelt his daughter, a passing fair and gracious damsel.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "He placed the ring in her hand, saying that he had done her will, as he was bidden to do.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "\"When the child is born,\" replied the lady, \"you must carry him forthwith to my sister.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "She is a rich dame, pitiful and good, and is wedded to a lord of Northumberland.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000013_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000013_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "You will send messages with the babe-both in writing and by speech-that the little innocent is her sister's child.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000013_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000013_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "Whether it be a boy or girl his mother will have suffered much because of him, and for her sister's sake you will pray her to cherish the babe.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000013_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000013_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "If this be done, perchance the orphan will not be fatherless all his days.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "The old nurse who tended her mistress was privy to the damsel's inmost mind.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000014_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000014_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "The child was then placed in his cradle, swathed close in white linen.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000014_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000014_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "The servitors set forth, bearing the infant with them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000014_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000014_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "They served their lord so faithfully, keeping such watch upon the way, that at the last they won to the lady to whom they were bidden.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000014_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000014_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "These having bestowed the boy in accordance with their lord's commandment, returned to their own land.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "Though this baron was a worthy knight, justly esteemed of all his fellows, the damsel was grieved beyond measure when she knew her father's will.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "So on the appointed day the lady was wedded to the baron, and her husband took her to dwell with him in his fief.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "He made him ready quickly, and went forth, bearing the swan with him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000020_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000020_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "He went by the nearest road, and passing through the streets of the city, came before the portal of the castle.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "\"Friend,\" said he, \"hearken to me.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "I am of Caerleon, and a fowler by craft.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "\"Friend,\" replied the porter, \"fowlers are not always welcomed of ladies.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "The porter entered in the hall, where he found none but two lords seated at a great table, playing chess for their delight.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000023_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000023_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "They went therefore to the chamber of the lady.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000023_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000023_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "When the swan was proffered to the lady it pleased her to receive the gift.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000023_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000023_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "She summoned a varlet of her household and gave the bird to his charge, commanding him to keep it safely, and to see that it ate enough and to spare.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000024_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000024_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "The swan is fit to serve at a royal table, for the bird is plump as he is fair.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "The varlet put the swan in his lady's hands.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "She took the bird kindly, and smoothing his head and neck, felt the letter that was hidden beneath its feathers.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000025_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000025_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "When they had parted the lady called a maiden to her aid. She broke the seal, and unfastening the letter, came upon the name of Milon at the head.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000025_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000025_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "She kissed the name a hundred times through her tears.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000025_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000025_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "In you-he wrote-is all my pleasure, and in your white hands it lies to heal me or to slay.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000025_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000025_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "Strive to find a plan by which we may speak as friend to friend, if you would have me live.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000025_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000025_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "The knight prayed her in his letter to send him an answer by means of the swan.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
