    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000026_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000026_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "She held him for a month within her chamber, but this was less from choice, than for the craft that was necessary to obtain the ink and parchment requisite for her writing.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000026_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000026_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "At the end she wrote a letter according to her heart, and sealed it with her ring.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000026_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000026_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "The lady caused the swan to fast for three full days; then having concealed the message about his neck, let him take his flight.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000027_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000027_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "Milon rejoiced greatly when he marked his own.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000027_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000027_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "He glanced from head to head of the letter, seeking the means that he hoped to find, and the salutation he so tenderly wished.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000028_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000028_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "There was no speech between them, save that carried by the bird.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000028_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000028_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "He to whom the letter came, saw to it that the messenger was fed to heart's desire.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000029_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000029_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "He rejoiced greatly to hear of his father's prowess, and was proud beyond measure of his renown.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000029_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000029_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "He considered within himself, saying to his own heart, that much should be required of his father's son, and that he would not be worthy of his blood if he did not endeavour to merit his name.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000029_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000029_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "He rode to Southampton, that he might find a ship equipped for sea, and so came to Barfleur.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000029_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000029_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "What he took from the rich he bestowed on such knights as were poor and luckless.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000029_000015",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000029_000015.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "These loved him greatly, since he gained largely and spent freely, granting of his wealth to all.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000029_000018",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000029_000018.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "Folk told how a certain knight from beyond the Humber, who had passed the sea in quest of wealth and honour, had so done, that by reason of his prowess, his liberality, and his modesty, men called him the Knight Peerless, since they did not know his name.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000030_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000030_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "He marvelled greatly that the stout spears of the past had not put on their harness and broken a lance for their ancient honour.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000030_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000030_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "One thing he determined, that he would cross the sea without delay, so that he might joust with the dansellon, and abate his pride.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000030_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000030_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "Milon caused his friend to know of his wishes.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000030_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000030_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "He opened out to her all his thought, and craved her permission to depart.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "She approved his desire to quit the realm for the sake of his honour, and far from putting let and hindrance in his path, trusted that in the end he would bring again her son.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000031_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000031_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "At that time a tournament was proclaimed to be held at Mont st Michel.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000031_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000031_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "Now in this tournament a knight could joust with that lord who was set over against him, or he could seek to break a lance with his chosen foe.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000031_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000031_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "But the Knight Peerless carried the cry from all his fellows, for none might stand before him, nor rival him in skill and address.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000031_000015",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000031_000015.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "Milon observed him curiously.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000031_000016",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000031_000016.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "The lad struck so heavily, he thrust home so shrewdly, that Milon's hatred changed to envy as he watched.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000031_000017",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000031_000017.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "Very comely showed the varlet, and much to Milon's mind.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000031_000019",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000031_000019.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "Milon struck his adversary so fiercely, that the lance splintered in his gauntlet; but the young knight kept his seat without even losing a stirrup.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "\"Sir,\" said he, \"I pray you to get upon your horse.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "Milon sprang upon his steed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "\"Friend,\" said he, \"hearken to me.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000034_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000034_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "I have seen much, and gone to and fro about the world.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000034_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000034_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "This day I am overthrown by a boy, and yet I cannot help but love thee.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000035_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000035_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "In hope and wish I purpose to cross the sea, and return to my own realm.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000036_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000036_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "He got him swiftly from his horse, and taking the lad by the fringe of his hauberk, he cried, \"Praise be to God, for now am I healed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000036_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000036_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "Fair friend, by my faith thou art my very son, for whom I came forth from my own land, and have sought through all this realm.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "The varlet climbed from the saddle, and stood upon his feet.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000037_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000037_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "Father and son kissed each other tenderly, with many comfortable words.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000037_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000037_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "Their love was fair to see, and those who looked upon their meeting, wept for joy and pity.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6258_49755_000038_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6258/49755/6258_49755_000038_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6258",
        "content": "They rode to their hostel, and with the knights of their fellowship, passed the hours in mirth and revelry.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
